title: 016: Alternative Medicine, Carbs, Muscle Memory, Overtraining & More
description: We posted a request for listener questions on Instagram (@mindpump) and you responded in force. In fact, we received so many questions that we couldn't begin to answer them all. So here is the first round of many more Q & A Friday episodes to come. If your question didn't make this episode, then just keep listening. We are bound to get to it in a future broadcast.
